      "content": "The correct answer is B) Force is equal to the change in momentum over time."
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Fantastic! You're absolutely right! Force is indeed equal to the change in momentum per unit time. You're doing an amazing job!"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for the quiz! I'm all done for now."
